title: Californians Move to Texas | Season 1 Commentary
description:
Can't get enough of the crazy antics of Steve & Timpani? We can't either, so we decided to cram into a room to talk about the antics behind the antics. Laugh with us, cry with us, or just remain entirely confused as to what we're even talking about.
